00:13:49,288 --> 00:13:50,789
Pooh cu, Pooh cu!

234
00:13:50,914 --> 00:13:53,542
- Grazie, Pooh.
- Congratulazioni!

235
00:13:53,667 --> 00:13:55,627
Hai vinto la gara.

236
00:13:55,752 --> 00:13:57,838
È Pooh

237
